setDetails.setDescription:
Want a set and forget portfolio based around the popularised BED portfolio concept. PBED covers this on Polygon with ETH, WBTC and DPI!

PBED has a twist on the conventional format where rebalances are discretionary based on momentum of the assets currently leading to try maximise returns.
setDetails.managerDescription: Crypto Kai is a crypto based content creator, community and core Set advocate. Come join us on YouTube and Discord where we document our Set investing journey!
